INSTALLATION

     To install Perl::Critic::Dynamic with C<make> give the following 
     commands to your favorite shell:

         tar -zxf Perl-Critic-Dynamic-0.04.tar.gz
         cd Perl-Critic-Dynamic-0.04
         perl Makefile.PL
         make
         make test
         make install 

     Or if you prefer C<Module::Build>, try this:

         tar -zxf Perl-Critic-Dynamic-0.04.tar.gz
         cd Perl-Critic-Dynamic-0.04
         perl Build.pl
         ./Build
         ./Build test
         ./Build install 
